00:37:59,430 --> 00:38:00,710
we need further investigation.

848
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:02,710
I suggest a temporary adjournment.

849
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,940
Given the major changes in this case,

850
00:38:04,950 --> 00:38:06,320
the court is adjourned.

851
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,860
This court is adjourned.

852
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:23,790
Mr. Xue.

853
00:38:23,810 --> 00:38:24,670
What does this mean?

854
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,330
Are they saying my sister wasn't killed by him?

855
00:38:26,330 --> 00:38:27,680
Now the court is adjourned.

856
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,900
The case is not over yet.

857
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,270
Why is it different

858
00:38:30,290 --> 00:38:31,190
than what you said before?

859
00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,000
Right.

860
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:33,890
You two go back first.

861
00:38:33,890 --> 00:38:36,150
Let me meet the judge with Mr. Chen first, alright?

862
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:36,880
Just go back.

863
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,600
Mr. Xue, you must tell the judge.

864
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:39,870
My sister can't have died in vain.

865
00:38:39,870 --> 00:38:40,490
Of course, I will.

866
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:41,010
Madam.

867
00:38:41,510 --> 00:38:42,240
Don't worry.

868
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:44,390
Thank you.

869
00:38:44,870 --> 00:38:45,530
No problem.

870
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:47,950
I'm sure that Wang Dafu will be declared not guilty

871
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:49,500
next time during the trial.

872
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:51,500
How will you explain this to the couple then?

873
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:53,990
If Wang Dafu is found not guilty, then the case will end.

874
00:38:53,990 --> 00:38:55,650
This 20,000 yuan is easy, huh?

875
00:38:57,310 --> 00:38:58,520
We still have 14,000 yuan left.

876
00:38:58,520 --> 00:38:59,780
You'll get 20%, 2,800.

877
00:38:59,910 --> 00:39:01,770
I'll give it to you after the deal is closed.

878
00:39:01,770 --> 00:39:02,320
Mr. Han.

879
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:08,260
Do you only care about money?

880
00:39:08,820 --> 00:39:10,480
Now that the murderer is gone,

881
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:13,190
and we can't win over the civil compensation.

882
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,990
You want the couple to pay 20,000 yuan.

883
00:39:14,990 --> 00:39:16,110
Do you think they'll accept that?

884
00:39:16,110 --> 00:39:17,240
I've done everything I could.

885
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:18,000
You've also come to support.

886
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:19,400
Put anything else aside,

887
00:39:19,470 --> 00:39:21,590
do you think they understand the spirit of a contract?

888
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:22,470
I do.

889
00:39:22,860 --> 00:39:24,830
Once you have received the service, no return of the money.

890
00:39:24,830 --> 00:39:25,600
Good for you.

891
00:39:25,630 --> 00:39:27,310
Today, the closely watched trial of Wang Dafu

892
00:39:27,310 --> 00:39:28,910
for intentional homicide

893
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,600
has officially started

894
00:39:30,630 --> 00:39:32,410
in the Jingbei City People's Court.

895
00:39:32,410 --> 00:39:34,010
Wang Dafu's lawyer

896
00:39:34,350 --> 00:39:35,270
submitted...

897
00:39:35,630 --> 00:39:36,850
Intern lawyer Luo.

898
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,070
Congratulations.

899
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:40,040
You're really amazing.

900
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:41,220
Congratulations for what?

901
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:43,440
If we hadn't found the alibi evidence,

902
00:39:43,470 --> 00:39:45,530
would you be busy counting money now?

903
00:39:45,530 --> 00:39:47,330
I heard you wanted 500,000 yuan.

904
00:39:47,830 --> 00:39:49,430
How much can you get from 500,000 yuan?

905
00:39:49,430 --> 00:39:52,360
Don't you feel guilty making money off this tragedy?

906
00:39:52,820 --> 00:39:54,270
Your achievement has been stolen,

907
00:39:54,270 --> 00:39:55,790
so you're taking it out on me, right?

908
00:39:55,790 --> 00:39:56,870
I've also suffered losses,

909
00:39:56,870 --> 00:39:58,110
and I haven't asked you for anything yet.

910
00:39:58,110 --> 00:39:59,080
What losses have you incurred?

911
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,270
What losses?

912
00:40:00,470 --> 00:40:02,070
This case should have been concluded today,

913
00:40:02,070 --> 00:40:02,950
but it hasn't.

914
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:04,190
So I'll have to come here several more times.

915
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:05,750
It'll take up a lot of my time,

916
00:40:05,750 --> 00:40:07,350
which is a loss.

917
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:08,910
Go away.

918
00:40:08,910 --> 00:40:10,330
I don't want to talk to a money-lover like you.

919
00:40:10,330 --> 00:40:11,330
It's disgusting.

920
00:40:11,510 --> 00:40:12,900
You're dressed so decently.

921
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:14,850
How can you be so uncivil in your speech?

922
00:40:14,850 --> 00:40:17,610
Vent your anger at your teacher, Han Zhitong.

923
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,000
I'm gonna go, Xue.

924
00:40:28,090 --> 00:40:28,750
Mr. Han.

925
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:29,630
Regarding the outlook for this case,

926
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:31,030
do you have any comments?

927
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:35,950
My client has

928
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:38,190
an undeniable and unquestionable alibi.

929
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:40,190
Mr. Han. I heard this is a pro bono case.

930
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:41,110
You worked so hard

931
00:40:41,110 --> 00:40:42,360
for a pro bono case?

932
00:40:43,200 --> 00:40:43,670
Yes.

933
00:40:43,910 --> 00:40:45,170
This is a pro bono case.

934
00:40:45,350 --> 00:40:46,090
In other words,

935
00:40:46,090 --> 00:40:47,590
I didn't charge a penny on this case.

936
00:40:47,590 --> 00:40:50,350
You're stepping on my toes and fishing for compliments.

937
00:40:50,350 --> 00:40:51,550
You're so shameless.

938
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:55,470
First of all, I didn't fish for compliments.

939
00:40:55,470 --> 00:40:57,730
I contributed more to this case than you.

940
00:40:58,120 --> 00:40:59,410
Second of all, Mr. Han asked me to come along.

941
00:40:59,410 --> 00:41:00,290
I had to come.

942
00:41:00,910 --> 00:41:01,990
When he asked me to be the lawyer,

943
00:41:01,990 --> 00:41:02,910
I called you,

944
00:41:02,910 --> 00:41:03,470
but you didn't answer the phone.

945
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:04,870
You can check your phone.

946
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:06,640
As for how you want to think about it, it's up to you.

947
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:07,520
I'm sorry, Ms. Qiu.

948
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:09,240
I didn't mean to target you.

949
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,190
It's okay.

950
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:11,720
I have my car with me.

951
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:12,960
I can give you a ride.

952
00:41:13,270 --> 00:41:13,870
It's okay.

953
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:15,370
I'll ride a shared bike.

954
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:25,870
What else do you want?

955
00:41:26,870 --> 00:41:28,870
I don't want anything. It's just...

956
00:41:29,750 --> 00:41:30,990
Without me,

957
00:41:30,990 --> 00:41:33,510
he wouldn't have made it.

958
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:34,630
Wang Dafu

959
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:36,490
may have been sentenced to death.

960
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:38,950
But when it came to appearing in court,

961
00:41:38,950 --> 00:41:39,790
he just hid it from me

962
00:41:39,790 --> 00:41:40,830
and got rid of me.

963
00:41:41,020 --> 00:41:43,650
How could he be so shameless?

964
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:46,590
You're still an intern lawyer.

965
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:49,990
You don't have the qualifications to go to court alone.

966
00:41:49,990 --> 00:41:51,150
From a procedural perspective,

967
00:41:51,150 --> 00:41:52,630
he did nothing wrong.

968
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:54,460
What else do you want?

969
00:41:58,250 --> 00:41:59,930
You were in a dilemma,

970
00:42:00,710 --> 00:42:02,380
and you insisted on investigating this case.

971
00:42:02,380 --> 00:42:03,180
Why?

972
00:42:03,510 --> 00:42:05,390
Was it for fame?

973
00:42:07,860 --> 00:42:08,470
Ms. Mei.

974
00:42:09,020 --> 00:42:10,550
I don't mind if you scold me.

975
00:42:10,750 --> 00:42:12,680
In fact, I kind of meant it that way.

976
00:42:14,060 --> 00:42:16,250
The more trapped I felt,

977
00:42:16,270 --> 00:42:18,110
the more I wanted to find a good case

978
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:19,270
to prove myself.

979
00:42:19,790 --> 00:42:21,070
I'm just that selfish.

980
00:42:21,670 --> 00:42:22,930
Well, it turns out that

981
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:25,720
I still haven't made a name for myself,

982
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,660
so I got annoyed.

983
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:32,630
You won't make significant progress in your legal career

984
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,820
if you're constantly distracted by other matters.

985
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:35,620
Well…

986
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:38,700
I just hope I can transition to a practicing lawyer.

987
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:42,310
By the way,

988
00:42:43,550 --> 00:42:44,350
a few days ago,

989
00:42:44,350 --> 00:42:46,710
Mr. Han told us about you.

990
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,710
What happened back then?

991
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:54,350
Someone hoped we'd fail.
